Class ChargeStatesFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.lsmbo.msda.recover.filters.ChargeStatesFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BasicFilter

    public class ChargeStatesFilter
extends java.lang.Object
implements BasicFilter
    This class provide information about charge states filter (getter and setter). filter spectrum according to his specific charge and charges we want to keep. Parameters used in this class are booleans. Spectrum will be kept according to value of these booleans.
